Package view.robotpanel

Contains all the robot panels.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandEditorPanel
    Represents the robot control panel, which is used to configure the moves.
    RobotComRenderer
    Renders RobotCom objects in a JList.
    RobotConnectionPanel
    Represents a panel used to set up and configure the connection to the Arduino.
    RobotMethodLoader
    This class loads the methods and annotations in the robot classes.
    RobotPanel
    A panel with a fancy title.
    RobotTerminal
    The panel used for sending commands to the robot.
